{"title":"以邻为壑（图片）","authors":["池北偶　陈封"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"以邻为壑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　陈封图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近几年来，美英等发达国家把数百万吨有毒有害的废料输出到了发展中国家，转嫁灾祸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪过，罪过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以邻为壑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残渣废料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有害糟粕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种垃圾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"视为奇货。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大量出口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污染他国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人遭殃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己安乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存心嫁祸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煞是缺德。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}